[SN]TITLE[SN]
Liam Nolan: Accrington Stanley sign Southport midfielder

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Accrington Stanley have signed Southport midfielder Liam Nolan for an undisclosed fee.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 22-year-old has become Stanley's first summer signing, agreeing a one-year contract with a one-year option.
"The aim has always been to get back into the Football League and I am made up to do it," former Crewe player Nolan told the League Two club's website.
As part of the deal, Stanley will face relegated National League side Southport in a friendly on 29 July.
